\begin_layout Section
Configuring the operating system 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
OpenHoldem requires specific system settings in order to correctly intuit
 the game state from the pixels on-screen, and to correctly take poker actions.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
\begin_inset Index
